[Episode 36]

3
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,519
Are you also in charge
of the Directorate of Palace Eunuchs?

4
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:47,839
Your Majesty,

5
00:01:48,559 --> 00:01:49,440
I don't know anything.

6
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,160
I really don't know anything, Your Majesty.

7
00:01:51,839 --> 00:01:52,480
It wasn't me.

8
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:53,959
Your Majesty!

9
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,680
I'm innocent.

10
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,319
I'm innocent!

11
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,720
I'm innocent, Your Majesty!

12
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,959
Your Majesty, I'm innocent!

13
00:01:59,279 --> 00:02:00,080
I'm innocent!

14
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:00,559
Your Majesty!

15
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:01,760
I'm innocent.

16
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:04,760
Your Majesty,

17
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:06,879
please speak for me.

18
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,279
I'm really innocent!

19
00:02:08,279 --> 00:02:08,880
Your Majesty!

20
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,320
Your Majesty!

21
00:02:10,559 --> 00:02:11,199
Your Majesty,

22
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,520
Yuan Qi has to attend

23
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,759
to your needs day and night.

24
00:02:14,279 --> 00:02:14,880
He's also responsible

25
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,440
for the tasks at the Directorate of Ceremonial.

26
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,479
He also temporarily supervises
the Directorate of Palace Eunuchs

27
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,720
because it's short of hands.

28
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,399
How can he handle so many things at once?

29
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,320
I'm sure

30
00:02:23,839 --> 00:02:24,720
Yuan Qi would never

31
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,880
have the nerve to...

32
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:27,000
Ignorant woman!

33
00:02:28,119 --> 00:02:29,000
How dare you speak blatantly.

34
00:02:29,839 --> 00:02:30,320
Leave!

35
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:31,759
Your Majesty,

36
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,320
is everything I say

37
00:02:35,679 --> 00:02:37,399
so unpleasant to you?

38
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,600
Yuan Qi.

39
00:02:51,399 --> 00:02:51,679
I'll go after

40
00:02:51,679 --> 00:02:52,839
Her Majesty right away.

41
00:02:52,839 --> 00:02:53,639
I didn't tell you to do that.

42
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:56,800
Liu Guan wanted to execute

43
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,039
seventy bandits, right?

44
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,160
Tell him to send the name list to me.

45
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:01,919
I want to reinvestigate it.

46
00:03:04,679 --> 00:03:05,320
Go now!

47
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,600
Your Majesty,

48
00:03:24,119 --> 00:03:25,240
you said you'd have a nice talk

49
00:03:25,559 --> 00:03:25,800
with His Majesty

50
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,479
when you visit him.

51
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,479
Why did you leave right away?

52
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,160
Empress Dowager always says

53
00:03:32,399 --> 00:03:33,399
we need to speak frankly

54
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,679
and give earnest advice
as the Empress and imperial concubines.

55
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,839
I spoke up for Yuan Qi

56
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:40,160
because I didn't want his anger
to affect his health.

57
00:03:41,119 --> 00:03:41,759
Moreover,

58
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,960
Yuan Qi had served him for many years.

59
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,360
There's bound to be some mutual affection.

60
00:03:45,119 --> 00:03:46,559
He scared him to such an extent.

61
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:47,880
How is he going to carry out
his tasks in the future?

62
00:03:49,839 --> 00:03:50,960
It's a pity that he doesn't heed my advice.

63
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:53,119
He can't bear the sight of me.

64
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,800
So everything I say is not pleasant to him.

65
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:18,279
Get lost.

66
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,079
I want all of you to get lost.

67
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,359
Your Majesty,

68
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,880
why are you losing your temper

69
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,239
out of a sudden?

70
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,519
The Empress is worried

71
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,559
about your health.

72
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,320
That's why she offered you advice.

73
00:04:54,359 --> 00:04:55,040
Why did you

74
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,200
chase her away?

75
00:04:57,119 --> 00:04:57,679
Yes.

76
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,279
All of you are right.

77
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,880
I'm the one at fault.

78
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,720
Leave. I don't want to see you either.

79
00:05:33,359 --> 00:05:34,000
Guards!

80
00:05:40,559 --> 00:05:41,480
His Majesty is unwell.

81
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:43,040
Get Imperial Physician Sheng.

82
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,079
I don't want to see anyone.

83
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,200
I forbid you to go.

84
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,480
Yuan Qi,

85
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:48,600
go now.

86
00:06:03,079 --> 00:06:04,720
Close your eyes and get some rest.

87
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,440
You'll be all right after taking your medicine.

88
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,239
I'll order

89
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,119
them not to come

90
00:06:11,119 --> 00:06:12,119
and bother you for now.

91
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,839
Sitting on this throne,

92
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,040
I must live up

93
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,480
to the predecessors of the Great Ming

94
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,679
and also don't let

95
00:06:34,679 --> 00:06:36,200
the people down.

96
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:38,480
Zijin.

97
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,720
It's hard on me.

98
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,440
Do you understand?

99
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,239
Did that really happen?

100
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,920
Your Majesty,

101
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,959
His Majesty smashed his cup in Qianqing Palace.

102
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,200
It could be heard from outside.

103
00:07:11,799 --> 00:07:13,279
Everyone in the palace is talking about it.

104
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,679
The Empress offered her sincere advice.

105
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,040
But it made His Majesty angry.

106
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,880
Instead,

107
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,760
His Majesty seems to prefer

108
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,640
the villain who's clever with flattering words.

109
00:07:25,679 --> 00:07:26,440
I was out of line.

110
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,559
Summon Noble Consort Sun.

111
00:07:34,119 --> 00:07:34,640
Yes, Your Majesty.

112
00:07:50,239 --> 00:07:50,799
Your Majesty.

113
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,119
I summoned you at noon.

114
00:07:55,119 --> 00:07:56,559
Why are you only here now?

115
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,440
Your Majesty,

116
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,519
I met

117
00:07:59,519 --> 00:08:01,519
Imperial Physician Sheng, who was summoned
by Qianqing Palace by chance

118
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:03,440
and found out His Majesty is unwell.

119
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,239
I was worried.

120
00:08:05,239 --> 00:08:06,160
So I asked about His Majesty's condition.

121
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,279
That's why I was late.

122
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,359
The Emperor is ill?

123
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,119
When did this happen?

124
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,440
Why did no one report this to me?

125
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:14,600
Please don't worry, Your Majesty.

126
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,239
Imperial Physician Sheng has said

127
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,399
His Majesty caught a cold.

128
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,200
It's nothing serious.

129
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,000
His Majesty fears you might worry.

130
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,600
So His Majesty ordered

131
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,200
not to trouble Qingning Palace.

132
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:26,640
His Majesty

133
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,920
is a filial son.

134
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,920
So they wouldn't dare to defy his edict.

135
00:08:31,279 --> 00:08:32,080
You can get up now.

136
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:33,960
Thank you, Your Majesty.

137
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,239
The Emperor is usually busy with state affairs.

138
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,320
So everyone

139
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,559
must be meticulous when attending to him.

140
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:41,919
How could no one notice

141
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,479
of such a serious matter?

142
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,320
It's my negligence.

143
00:08:47,479 --> 00:08:48,039
Never mind.

144
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,359
It's not entirely your fault.

145
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:51,760
There are

146
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,559
too many problems in the palace.

147
00:08:54,159 --> 00:08:55,599
The Empress is always sick.

148
00:08:56,239 --> 00:08:58,239
So you're taking all of the responsibility.

149
00:08:58,239 --> 00:08:59,559
It's hard for you to manage
so many things at once.

150
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:01,880
Is there anyone

151
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,239
in the imperial harem

152
00:09:04,239 --> 00:09:06,039
who can share your burden?

153
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:08,960
Since Your Majesty asked,

154
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:11,520
I'll speak without fear.

155
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,159
Previously,

156
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:15,159
the Empress had been sick.

157
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:17,520
So I had to handle palace affairs on her behalf.

158
00:09:18,239 --> 00:09:20,640
But the Empress has recovered.

159
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,960
It's right for her to manage the imperial harem.

160
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:26,000
The Empress is weak in health.

161
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:28,239
She'd often fall sick now and then.

162
00:09:28,599 --> 00:09:29,599
The palace affairs are cumbersome

163
00:09:29,599 --> 00:09:30,599
with complicated people.

164
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,359
It's not easy to manage.

165
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,280
Aren't you putting her in a difficult position?

166
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:35,760
Your Majesty,

167
00:09:36,599 --> 00:09:37,479
the Empress

168
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,760
is generous, benevolent, and righteous.

169
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:40,960
Even if

170
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,039
a servant made a mistake,

171
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,760
Her Majesty doesn't have
the heart to punish them.

172
00:09:44,599 --> 00:09:45,840
It's the blessing of the imperial harem

173
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,039
and the Great Ming.

174
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:50,280
It's just that Her Majesty has just recovered.

175
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,440
It's not advisable for her to overwork.

176
00:09:52,239 --> 00:09:54,880
How about requesting
Gracious Consort He to assist?

177
00:09:55,559 --> 00:09:56,440
She's been in the palace the longest.

178
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,280
She's capable and intelligent.

179
00:09:58,359 --> 00:09:59,280
She also handles things appropriately.

180
00:10:00,719 --> 00:10:01,960
Among the imperial concubines,

181
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,320
Lady Wu is the most talkative.

182
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,039
She would gossip

183
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,200
about you in front of others.

184
00:10:06,719 --> 00:10:08,919
I want to punish her severely. What do you think?

185
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:10,960
Lady of Bright Deportment Wu

186
00:10:11,479 --> 00:10:12,440
is still young.

187
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,719
So she's a lively girl.

188
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:17,719
But I'm sure she meant no harm.

189
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:20,200
His Majesty happens to order people
to create Xuande incense burner.

190
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:22,760
But the designs produced by the craftsmen

191
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,760
are not to His Majesty's liking.

192
00:10:24,599 --> 00:10:26,280
Since Lady of Bright Deportment Wu
loves incense,

193
00:10:26,599 --> 00:10:28,559
why not send her to supervise this matter?

194
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:30,320
It's what she likes,

195
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,320
and she can help His Majesty solve a problem.

196
00:10:33,479 --> 00:10:34,400
Also...

197
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:36,159
Go on.

198
00:10:37,359 --> 00:10:38,239
Since the Hongwu Reign,

199
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,640
Hongwu Emperor created

200
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,520
the Six Services based on
the Tang and Song Dynasties

201
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,320
for female officials to manage
the palace affairs.

202
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:44,559
But the female officials

203
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:46,039
lost their power after a while.

204
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:47,760
Many palace eunuchs

205
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:50,039
indulged in power and greed.

206
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:51,719
Matron Meng

207
00:10:51,719 --> 00:10:53,679
took back the power overnight.

208
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:54,760
All affairs in the imperial harem

209
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:56,039
must be reported to their superiors

210
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,799
regardless of big or small.

211
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:00,799
Let's put aside the Empress, who's frail.

212
00:11:01,719 --> 00:11:02,760
It's even difficult for me

213
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,080
to manage everything.

214
00:11:04,799 --> 00:11:05,919
You were saying all these

215
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,320
because you want to restore the old system.

216
00:11:08,559 --> 00:11:09,159
Your Majesty,

217
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:10,960
female officials always carry

218
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,919
heavy responsibilities.

219
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,719
In my opinion,

220
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,440
Cao Jieyu is a meticulous person.

221
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,760
She can manage the Imperial Ceremonial Service.

222
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,919
Worthy Lady Jiao is good at needlework.

223
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:22,239
She can manage the Palace Workshop Service.

224
00:11:22,679 --> 00:11:24,559
As for Lady Xu and Lady Yuan,

225
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,719
they love clothes and adornments.

226
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:27,880
It would be best

227
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:29,200
if they could manage
the Imperial Wardrobe Service.

228
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:30,919
It's not against the old practice either.

229
00:11:31,479 --> 00:11:33,440
Every Six Services has persons in charge.

230
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,280
The imperial concubines only need
to pay more attention

231
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,599
and pick out important matters

232
00:11:37,599 --> 00:11:38,640
to report to the Empress.

233
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:42,000
When imperial concubines have their own duties,

234
00:11:42,359 --> 00:11:43,679
there will be less fighting
over the Emperor's attention.

235
00:11:44,239 --> 00:11:45,640
The female officials will also have
someone to rely on.

236
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,039
That way, they'd focus more on their tasks.

237
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,200
Then the imperial harem
would naturally be in peace.

238
00:11:51,479 --> 00:11:53,159
Only the Palace Surveillance
will be responsible

239
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:55,039
for maintaining discipline

240
00:11:55,119 --> 00:11:56,080
and punishment.

241
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:58,440
This matter can't be put in the hands of others.

242
00:11:58,880 --> 00:11:59,679
The Empress

243
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:00,840
must attend to this in person.

244
00:12:01,479 --> 00:12:03,239
It's also up to the Empress to reward or punish

245
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:05,280
those who manage the Six Services.

246
00:12:06,159 --> 00:12:07,760
If someone is not competent enough,

247
00:12:08,119 --> 00:12:09,559
we can choose someone else
to take over in the following year.

248
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:13,039
So you're saying

249
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:14,679
to give everyone something to do,

250
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,719
so they don't

251
00:12:15,719 --> 00:12:17,440
have the time to stir up trouble.

252
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,799
You haven't finished
what you said just now, right?

253
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:22,840
Yes.

254
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:24,640
There are some candidates

255
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,280
that I can't decide on.

256
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:27,880
I ask that Your Majesty decide on it.

257
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:29,799
I understand.

258
00:12:30,239 --> 00:12:31,400
If we want them to work seriously,

259
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:34,640
we'll have to promote them.

260
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:36,400
Your Majesty is wise.

261
00:12:39,599 --> 00:12:41,760
There's one more thing that I want to report.

262
00:12:42,119 --> 00:12:42,640
What is it?

263
00:12:43,359 --> 00:12:44,520
This year, Kaiping wants

264
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,359
to reward its soldiers at the border.

265
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:47,919
But

266
00:12:47,919 --> 00:12:49,280
the cotton cloth needed for winter clothes

267
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:50,520
is not enough.

268
00:12:51,359 --> 00:12:52,520
I know there's some unused cloth

269
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:54,080
in the storehouse.

270
00:12:54,559 --> 00:12:55,679
I ask that Your Majesty
give me some instructions.

271
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,200
All right.

272
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,159
I'll take my leave now.

273
00:13:01,559 --> 00:13:02,119
Go.

274
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,159
Come out.

275
00:13:26,119 --> 00:13:26,960
Lady of Bright Deportment Wu,

276
00:13:28,919 --> 00:13:30,119
did you hear that?

277
00:13:30,359 --> 00:13:30,880
Your Majesty,

278
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,119
a person who does good

279
00:13:32,119 --> 00:13:33,039
for fame

280
00:13:33,039 --> 00:13:34,119
is the real bad person.

281
00:13:34,559 --> 00:13:34,960
No.

282
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:35,960
People usually

283
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,159
call such a person a hypocrite.

