00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:02,400
So she especially comes to visit it.

572
00:32:07,560 --> 00:32:08,439
How pitiful.

573
00:32:09,520 --> 00:32:10,800
You can even say when you're hurting.

574
00:32:12,319 --> 00:32:13,319
If I knew,

575
00:32:14,119 --> 00:32:15,359
I'd rather have you run away from me

576
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,079
than see you sick.

577
00:32:19,280 --> 00:32:20,599
I'll take it back to take care of it.

578
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:24,599
Go and prepare.

579
00:32:26,839 --> 00:32:27,439
Yes, Your Majesty.

580
00:32:34,359 --> 00:32:35,000
Imperial Physician Sheng.

581
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:36,680
Noble Consort Sun,

582
00:32:37,439 --> 00:32:39,119
His Majesty is vexed from fever,

583
00:32:39,359 --> 00:32:40,239
thirst, and fatigue.

584
00:32:40,839 --> 00:32:42,920
The summer heat causes all these.

585
00:32:43,239 --> 00:32:43,719
Put it down.

586
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:45,119
I'll prescribe

587
00:32:45,119 --> 00:32:47,000
Liuyi Powder to dispel and clear heat.

588
00:32:47,599 --> 00:32:49,319
He'll be fine after two to three days.

589
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:51,199
All right.

590
00:32:52,359 --> 00:32:53,119
I'll prepare the prescription.

591
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:06,800
Fu Jiang,

592
00:33:07,359 --> 00:33:08,839
is Yantai feeling better now?

593
00:33:09,760 --> 00:33:11,199
The Empress went to the study.

594
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,760
She said she'll take care of it.

595
00:33:14,719 --> 00:33:15,640
Why don't we take it back?

596
00:33:17,479 --> 00:33:18,239
Her Majesty

597
00:33:18,239 --> 00:33:19,520
truly loves Yantai.

598
00:33:20,359 --> 00:33:21,920
We'll have to trouble her
to take care of it these two days.

599
00:33:23,359 --> 00:33:24,560
Later, I'll list down

600
00:33:25,119 --> 00:33:25,920
some of Yantai's

601
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,560
favorite things to be sent over.

602
00:33:30,280 --> 00:33:31,680
You've been up for days.

603
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,400
Why don't you get some rest?

604
00:33:33,760 --> 00:33:34,680
When His Majesty is awake,

605
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,880
I'll wake you up.

606
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:37,439
He'll ask

607
00:33:38,599 --> 00:33:39,920
if today's memorials

608
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:41,160
are sent over

609
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,439
when he wakes up.

610
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,520
Where are the memorials?

611
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:49,640
Your Majesty.

612
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:53,719
Yuan Qi.

613
00:33:54,239 --> 00:33:54,719
Yes, Your Majesty.

614
00:34:33,879 --> 00:34:34,879
From tonight onward,

615
00:34:34,959 --> 00:34:37,280
all memorials from the Office of Transmission

616
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:38,239
will be handed over

617
00:34:38,239 --> 00:34:39,520
to Yang Shiqi to read

618
00:34:39,840 --> 00:34:40,439
and draw a conclusion

619
00:34:40,439 --> 00:34:41,479
before sending them to Qianqing Palace.

620
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:42,679
Yes, Your Majesty.

621
00:34:57,280 --> 00:34:58,040
Huaping,

622
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,320
get my medicine box.

623
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:03,760
Huaping,

624
00:35:04,679 --> 00:35:05,800
I want to save it.

625
00:35:06,439 --> 00:35:07,199
Your Majesty,

626
00:35:07,639 --> 00:35:08,280
this is His Majesty's

627
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,560
favorite pet.

628
00:35:10,159 --> 00:35:11,600
He spoils it every day.

629
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:12,719
We can't take the risk.

630
00:35:12,719 --> 00:35:13,719
You heard

631
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,239
how it cried sadly at night.

632
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,320
I want to give it a try.

633
00:35:21,439 --> 00:35:22,399
Even if there's a glimmer of hope,

634
00:35:22,399 --> 00:35:23,520
I still want to save it.

635
00:35:27,560 --> 00:35:29,399
Does Her Majesty know how to treat a cat?

636
00:35:31,679 --> 00:35:32,840
Her Majesty said

637
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:34,520
this medicine is specially prepared for Yantai,

638
00:35:34,520 --> 00:35:35,479
and it has a pain-relieving effect.

639
00:35:35,520 --> 00:35:36,800
We must not let anyone consume it by mistake.

640
00:35:36,879 --> 00:35:38,479
Life and death are natural orders.

641
00:35:39,159 --> 00:35:40,159
It's the same with a cat.

642
00:35:41,199 --> 00:35:43,439
Why must we use medicine to prolong its life?

643
00:36:34,919 --> 00:36:35,959
This vegetarian food smells good.

644
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:38,560
No, it's not.

645
00:36:40,959 --> 00:36:42,120
What's wrong with you today?

646
00:37:00,520 --> 00:37:01,120
Your Majesty,

647
00:37:01,439 --> 00:37:02,560
the vegetarian dishes

648
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:03,639
for the Zhongyuan Festival are ready.

649
00:37:06,239 --> 00:37:07,719
Deliver the dishes to His Majesty
and the Empress Dowager first

650
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:09,080
before delivering them to the imperial harem.

651
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:10,280
Yes, Your Majesty.

652
00:37:30,439 --> 00:37:32,199
Your Majesty's illness has improved greatly.

653
00:37:32,399 --> 00:37:33,800
But you haven't eaten

654
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:34,800
since noon yesterday.

655
00:37:35,080 --> 00:37:36,399
I'm afraid you might suffer from a heat stroke.

656
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,360
Your body won't be able to stand it.

657
00:37:39,199 --> 00:37:40,520
I've sent someone to prepare your meal.

658
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:42,239
Please have some before getting some rest.

659
00:37:43,239 --> 00:37:44,159
I'm not hungry.

660
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:45,239
I have no appetite.

661
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:47,320
Your Highness.

662
00:37:48,639 --> 00:37:49,439
Noble Consort Sun,

663
00:37:50,719 --> 00:37:51,760
today is Zhongyuan Festival.

664
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:53,840
The Empress had prepared vegetarian dishes

665
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:54,760
for everyone in the imperial harem.

666
00:37:55,879 --> 00:37:56,719
I can smell its aroma

667
00:37:56,719 --> 00:37:58,040
from the food box.

668
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:00,479
Your Majesty.

669
00:39:00,719 --> 00:39:01,919
Your arrogance

670
00:39:02,600 --> 00:39:03,840
almost killed me.

671
00:39:04,959 --> 00:39:05,719
You won't even

672
00:39:05,719 --> 00:39:06,919
let Zijin go this time?

673
00:39:16,919 --> 00:39:17,959
I don't understand what you're saying.

674
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:20,479
Yuan Qi.

675
00:39:20,560 --> 00:39:21,040
Your Majesty.

676
00:39:21,959 --> 00:39:23,320
Send the Empress back to Kunning Palace.

677
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:24,560
Without my order,

678
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:25,760
she's not to leave the palace.

679
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:26,639
Yes, Your Majesty.

680
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:28,399
Your Majesty,

681
00:39:28,959 --> 00:39:30,080
what did I do wrong?

682
00:39:30,399 --> 00:39:31,879
You should give me a chance to explain.

683
00:39:32,719 --> 00:39:33,199
Your Majesty.

684
00:39:33,199 --> 00:39:33,879
Your Majesty,

685
00:39:34,719 --> 00:39:35,840
His Majesty is furious now.

686
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:37,520
Please say no more.

687
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:38,719
Please return to your palace.

688
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:18,639
Your Majesty,

689
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,479
I've known the Empress for many years.

690
00:40:20,479 --> 00:40:21,520
I know her very well.

691
00:40:21,919 --> 00:40:23,040
She would never do something like this.

692
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:23,840
But...

693
00:40:28,719 --> 00:40:29,879
I bear firmly in my mind

694
00:40:29,879 --> 00:40:31,120
what you've taught me.

695
00:40:32,479 --> 00:40:33,360
But this concerns the Empress.

696
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,479
I dare not keep it a secret.

697
00:40:34,959 --> 00:40:35,479
Noble Consort Sun

698
00:40:35,479 --> 00:40:37,040
has always been on good terms
with Directress Yin.

699
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,679
How do we know if they didn't plot

700
00:40:38,679 --> 00:40:39,679
to gain sympathy?

701
00:40:42,479 --> 00:40:44,159
Your Majesty, Directress Yin is here.

702
00:40:44,679 --> 00:40:45,399
Summon her.

703
00:40:45,639 --> 00:40:46,120
Yes, Your Majesty.

704
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:55,159
Greetings, Your Majesty.

705
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:56,080
Rise.

706
00:40:59,479 --> 00:41:00,320
I'd like to hear

707
00:41:01,159 --> 00:41:01,800
your opinion

708
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,120
on what happened today.

709
00:41:03,239 --> 00:41:03,800
Your Majesty,

710
00:41:04,719 --> 00:41:06,280
Her Majesty is a kind person.

711
00:41:06,639 --> 00:41:08,199
To relieve Yantai from pain,

712
00:41:08,679 --> 00:41:10,719
Her Majesty ordered me
to add medicine to the cat's food.

713
00:41:11,239 --> 00:41:12,840
I did as I was ordered.

714
00:41:13,520 --> 00:41:14,520
After that...

715
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:22,479
(Because the medicine bottle
is from Kunning Palace,)

716
00:41:22,840 --> 00:41:23,879
(I was afraid someone might eat it by mistake)

717
00:41:23,879 --> 00:41:24,840
(or dispute about it.)

718
00:41:25,199 --> 00:41:26,399
(So I got rid of it right away.)

719
00:41:27,560 --> 00:41:28,719
Everyone at the Imperial Food Service

720
00:41:29,040 --> 00:41:30,639
was busy preparing vegetarian dishes
because it was Zhongyuan Festival.

721
00:41:31,199 --> 00:41:32,800
I was going to report it the next day.

722
00:41:33,399 --> 00:41:34,280
But I didn't expect

723
00:41:34,520 --> 00:41:35,959
Noble Consort Sun would vomit blood
and fainted that night.

724
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:37,439
I was reminded of the medicine.

725
00:41:37,679 --> 00:41:39,320
So I checked under the peach blossom tree.

726
00:41:39,879 --> 00:41:42,280
Someone had indeed stolen it.

727
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:44,399
Do you think

728
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:46,840
Noble Consort Sun's serious illness

729
00:41:47,479 --> 00:41:48,679
has anything to do with Kunning Palace?

730
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,439
Noble Consort Sun is unconscious,

731
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:53,280
and the Empress becomes the suspect.

732
00:41:53,919 --> 00:41:55,639
If we look at the intention
of the person behind this,

733
00:41:55,959 --> 00:41:57,199
it's to drive a wedge between them

734
00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:58,080
and bring chaos to the imperial harem.

735
00:41:58,639 --> 00:41:59,800
I'm more worried

736
00:42:00,159 --> 00:42:01,439
that the Emperor would wrongfully

737
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,840
accuse the Empress out of rage.

738
00:42:03,600 --> 00:42:04,360
If I may be bold,

739
00:42:04,560 --> 00:42:05,919
I hope Your Majesty would take
this matter into your hand

740
00:42:06,399 --> 00:42:07,239
and protect the Empress.

741
00:42:08,159 --> 00:42:09,800
You said it in such a sensible manner.

742
00:42:10,879 --> 00:42:11,800
Who taught you to say that?
